0a0(Cap 20)</h2>\n<div>\n<div>For time:</div>\n<div>70 Wall Balls 20/14#</div>\n<div>70 Burpees</div>\n<div>70 Stepdown Box Jumps 24/20#</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<hr>\n<p>This MetCon might look simple. Conditioning doesn\u2019t have to be complicated to work and often it is the combination of movements that make it difficult. Wall Balls, Burpees and Box Jumps are all global and metabolically stressful movements. Combined they create a great test of conditioning.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
