{"all": "<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-for-thursday-42717\"><span class=\"post-featured-img\"><img width=\"660\" height=\"496\" src=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-13-at-6.02.41-PM.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" srcset=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-13-at-6.02.41-PM.png 660w, http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-13-at-6.02.41-PM-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"></span></a>\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"article-content-wrap\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"post-header\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-for-thursday-42717\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWOD for Thursday, 4/27/17\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t </a> \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"meta-author\"><span>By</span> <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/author/tewf\" title=\"Posts by Dan Tewfik\" rel=\"author\">Dan Tewfik</a></span> <span class=\"meta-category\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/strength-programming\">Strength Programming</a>, <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/wod\">WOD</a></span> <span class=\"meta-comment-count\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-for-thursday-42717#respond\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tNo Comments</a></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--/post-header-->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Strength: (20mins)</h2>\n<p>Deadlifts:<br>\nWeek 5<br>\n5\u00d73 @85% of Week 1</p>\n<h2>MetCon: (Cap 18)</h2>\n<p>For time:<br>\n400m Run<br>\n-then 3 rounds of:<br>\n10 Deadlift @ 225/155#<br>\n10 Bar Hop Burpees (parallel)<br>\n-then<br>\n400m Run</p>\n<p>Today\u2019s MetCon is a running sandwich with dea