un and 15 overhead squats. At first it doesn\u2019t seem too bad but as the rounds add up your breathing, core and shoulders get taxed and what seemed to be a light squat gets much harder.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
