n200m Walking Lunge<br>\n*scale distance and volume for less conditioned athletes.</p>\n<p>In honor of the distance traveled by the participants of the Boston Marathon and the struggle they endure during the race I created a challenging and unique workout. \u201cMarathon Monday\u201d was our first workout that was entirely locomotive but it is still unique in the way that you must move in various ways, caring various objects. I\u2019m really looking forward to see how people do on this.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
