ight used will serve as a baseline for the program moving forward.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength:</h2>\n<p><strong>Week 1: Deadlift </strong><br>\n5\u00d71 AHAP *all at the same weight</p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>AMRAP 13</strong><br>\n15 Deadlifts 135/95#<br>\n20 Overhead Stepback Lunges w/ MB 20/14#<br>\n25 Russian Twists w/ MB</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
