n12 Ring Rows<br>\n20 Shoulder Taps</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/2NGH8jayP8I\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2NGH8jayP8I</a></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p>As many reps as possible of:</p>\n<p>1min Wall Balls 20/14#<br>\n1min Push-ups<br>\n1min Cal Row<br>\n2min Wall Balls<br>\n2min Push-ups<br>\n2min Cal Row<br>\n3min Wall Balls<br>\n3min Push-ups<br>\n3min Cal Row</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
