{"all": "<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-031017\"><span class=\"post-featured-img\"><img width=\"694\" height=\"522\" src=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Screen-Shot-2017-03-06-at-2.37.04-PM.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" srcset=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Screen-Shot-2017-03-06-at-2.37.04-PM.png 694w, http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Screen-Shot-2017-03-06-at-2.37.04-PM-300x226.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 694px) 100vw, 694px\"></span></a>\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"article-content-wrap\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"post-header\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-031017\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWOD for Friday, 3/10/17\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t </a> \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"meta-author\"><span>By</span> <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/author/admin\" title=\"Posts by CrossFit on the Hill\" rel=\"author\">CrossFit on the Hill</a></span> <span class=\"meta-category\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/stability\">Stability</a>, <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/wod\">WOD</a></span> <span class=\"meta-comment-count\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-031017#respond\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tNo Comments</a></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--/post-header-->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Today\u2019s strength portion of class is focusing on the Clean and Jerk movements with a Barbell Complex. Complexes are great for building overall strength and technique. By extending the time you are handling the barbell you are increasing your body\u2019s time under tension and global strength. Then, we will finish the week with a sprint chipper so we can work on our short time domain conditioning.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Skill:</h2>\n<p><strong>Hang Squat Clean</strong></p>\n<h2>Strength:</h2>\n<p><em>*10 mins to establish 1RM of the following complex:</em><br>\n1 Power Clean<br>\n1 Hang Squat Clean<br>\n1 Jerk (any type)</p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>Sprint Chipper:</strong><br>\n1k Row<br>\n25 Sit-ups<br>\n25 Thrusters 45/35#</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
