 Rows<br>\n12 Banded Face Pulls<br>\n10 Single Leg RDL (each)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/HHGivxXIqEs\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HHGivxXIqEs</a></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201cAnchorman\u201d</strong><br>\n21/15/9<br>\nDeadlifts 275/195#<br>\nChest to Bar</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
