{"all": "<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-030717\"><span class=\"post-featured-img\"><img width=\"695\" height=\"440\" src=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Screen-Shot-2017-03-06-at-2.24.44-PM.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" srcset=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Screen-Shot-2017-03-06-at-2.24.44-PM.png 695w, http://crossfitonthehill.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Screen-Shot-2017-03-06-at-2.24.44-PM-300x190.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 695px) 100vw, 695px\"></span></a>\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"article-content-wrap\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"post-header\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-030717\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWOD for Tuesday, 3/07/17\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t </a> \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"meta-author\"><span>By</span> <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/author/admin\" title=\"Posts by CrossFit on the Hill\" rel=\"author\">CrossFit on the Hill</a></span> <span class=\"meta-category\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/skill\">Skill</a>, <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/wod\">WOD</a></span> <span class=\"meta-comment-count\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-030717#respond\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tNo Comments</a></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--/post-header-->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Multi-planar movements are essential to be a complete athlete. This requires us to train in the Sagittal, Transverse, and Frontal planes. This 20 minute AMRAP is a good example of multi-planar training. It\u2019s also a good example of bodyweight and loaded exercises.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Skill:</h2>\n<p><strong>HSPU</strong><br>\n5 Rounds:<br>\n30 sec Handstand or Head Stand Hold<br>\n30sec rest</p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>AMRAP 20</strong><br>\n20 MB Russian Twists 20/14#<br>\n10 Front Squat 185/120#<br>\n5 Wall Climb</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
