ent:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/2wPTwOV5m78\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2wPTwOV5m78</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201c17.2\u2033</strong></p>\n<p>Complete as many rounds and reps as possible in 12 minutes of:</p>\n<p>2 rounds of:<br>\n50-ft. weighted walking lunge 50/35#<br>\n16 toes-to-bars<br>\n8 power cleans</p>\n<p>Then, 2 rounds of:<br>\n50-ft. weighted walking lunge<br>\n16 bar muscle-ups<br>\n8 power cleans</p>\n<p>*All details at:<br>\n<a href=\"https://games.crossfit.com/workouts/open/2017\" target=\"_blank\">https://games.crossfit.com/workouts/open/2017</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
