ficult and unilateral imbalances will be more prevalent.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength: (10mins)</h2>\n<p>Establish 5RM Strict Press</p>\n<h2>Skill:</h2>\n<p><strong>DB Hang Clean</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/loJGqTGkXEo?list=PLdWvFCOAvyr0hDT1uP507BWGn35BX7U0G\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/loJGqTGkXEo?list=PLdWvFCOAvyr0hDT1uP507BWGn35BX7U0G</a></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>5 RFR:</strong><br>\n40sec ME Cal Row<br>\n-20sec Rest<br>\n40sec ME DB Hang Clean 50/35#<br>\n-20sec Rest<br>\n40sec ME Toes to Bar<br>\n-20sec Rest</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
