{"all": "<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"article-content-wrap\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"post-header\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-020817\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWOD for Wednesday, 2/08/17\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t </a> \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"meta-author\"><span>By</span> <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/author/admin\" title=\"Posts by CrossFit on the Hill\" rel=\"author\">CrossFit on the Hill</a></span> <span class=\"meta-category\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/skill\">Skill</a>, <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/strength-programming\">Strength Programming</a>, <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/category/wod\">WOD</a></span> <span class=\"meta-comment-count\">| <a href=\"http://crossfitonthehill.com/wod/wod-020817#respond\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tNo Comments</a></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--/post-header-->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This is Week 4 of our Power Snatch Program. This will be the heaviest week before deloading next week and maxing out the following week just in time for the 2017 CrossFit Open to start. I hope your skill and technique is coming together.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Skill:</h2>\n<p>3-Part Pause Snatch (Start, Knee, Hips)</p>\n<p>10x 3 Part Pause  Power Snatch<br>\n10x 2 Part Pause Power Snatch (Knee / Hips)<br>\n10x 1 Part Pause Power Snatch (Knee)<br>\n10x Power Snatch (Slow to Knee but no pause)</p>\n<h2>Strength: (20mins)</h2>\n<p><strong>Power Snatch</strong><br>\nWeek 4: 3@50%, 3@60%, 3@70%, 3@75%, 3@80%, 3@85%, 3@90% of (# from Week 1)</p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>For time: (Cap 10)</strong><br>\n3 RFT:<br>\n9 Front Squats 185/135#<br>\n15 Sit-ups<br>\n21 Alternating DB Snatch 50/35#</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
