ue exercises.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength / Skill: (10mins)</h2>\n<p><strong>Pistol Progression 1:</strong><br>\n4\u00d710 (each) Single Leg Squat Off Box</p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201cDanny\u201d</strong><br>\nAMRAP 12<br>\n30 DU\u2019s / 90 singles<br>\n20 OverHead Walking lunges #45/35 plate<br>\n10 Ring Push-ups/ HR Push-ups</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
