2-3 warm-up sets prior to 5 working sets.</em></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>4 RFR: (15mins)</strong><br>\n1min ME Cal Row<br>\n1min ME Pull-ups<br>\n1min ME Box Jumps 24/20#<br>\n1min Rest</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
