ble up and pair that format with a quadruplet!</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Stability:</h2>\n<p><strong>Hanging Hollow Position</strong><br>\n5\u00d730:30sec</p>\n<h2>Skill: (6mins)</h2>\n<p><strong>Chest to Bar</strong></p>\n<h2>MetCon: (Cap 20)</h2>\n<p><strong>For time:</strong><br>\n21/15/9<br>\nThruster 95/65#<br>\nHang Power Clean<br>\nFront Squat<br>\nChest to Bar</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
