move from movement to movement. This is a high scoring CrossFit WOD.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength:</h2>\n<p><strong>4Rounds</strong><br>\n12 Single Arm DB Row<br>\n1 Lap DB Waiters Walk<br>\nPlank w/ reach (20 alternating touches)</p>\n<p>Waiters walk:<br>\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Th41Un1J6oQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Th41Un1J6oQ</a></p>\n<p>Plank w/reach:<br>\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lfVAjy16i2w\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lfVAjy16i2w</a></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201c13.2\u2033</strong><br>\nAMRAP 10<br>\n5 Shoulder to Overhead 115/75#<br>\n10 Deadlift 115/75#<br>\n15 Box Jumps 24/20\u2033</p>\n<p>All other details:<br>\n<a href=\"http://games.crossfit.com/workouts/the-open/2013\" target=\"_blank\">http://games.crossfit.com/workouts/the-open/2013</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
