ighted Step-ups (each)<br>\n10 Single Leg RDL (each)<br>\n5 Dragon Flags</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/zFapgeXigLk\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zFapgeXigLk</a></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>AMRAP 10</strong><br>\n20 Walking Boulder Lunges 20/14#<br>\n20 MB Slams<br>\n-but Starting w/ and EMOTM 5 Burpees</p>\n<p><em>*burpees do not count in the score</em></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
