19t just expect you to survive the workout but work to improve at all movements included. We will also be taking extra class time each week to work on progressing some of the more difficult but common CrossFit movement such as a Toe to Bar.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Skill: (10 mins)</h2>\n<p><strong>Toes to Bar</strong></p>\n<p><em>*List of CrossFit\u2019s T2B videos:</em><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/CrossFitHQ/search?query=toes+to+bar\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/CrossFitHQ/search?query=toes+to+bar</a></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201c11.5\u2033</strong><br>\nAMRAP 20<br>\n5 Power Cleans (145/100#)<br>\n10 Toes to Bar<br>\n15 Wall Balls 20/14#</p>\n<p>All other variations / details:<br>\n<a href=\"http://games.crossfit.com/workouts/the-open/2011\" target=\"_blank\">http://games.crossfit.com/workouts/the-open/2011</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
