test for those who have participated in the Open before or provide an example of what workouts like for those new to the Open.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength: (12 minutes)</h2>\n<p><strong>5RM Push Press</strong><br>\n*minimum 4 sets total</p>\n<h2>Metcon</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201c16.4\u2033</strong><br>\nAMRAP 13<br>\n55 deadlifts 225/155#<br>\n55 wall-ball shots 20/14#<br>\n55-calorie row<br>\n55 handstand push-ups (probably not enough time to set up Open standards)</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
