 on to the next. Your variety of movements include the knee dominant Wall Ball, the hip dominant KB Swing and the anterior chain dominant Toes to Bar.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Warm-up:</h2>\n<p>5x (across and back)<br>\nIn-line Bear Crawl</p>\n<h2>MetCon: (18-20 mins)</h2>\n<p><strong>EMOTM 6 </strong><br>\n15 Wall Balls (Beginner 10 reps)<br>\n-1min rest<br>\n<strong>EMOTM 6</strong><br>\n20 KB swing (1.5/1) (Beginner 15 reps)<br>\n-1min rest<br>\n<strong>EMOTM 6</strong><br>\n8 T2B (15 K2C) (Beginner 15 Sit-ups)<br>\n-1min rest</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
