ween the elbow and feet.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength Circuit:</h2>\n<p><strong>3 Rounds:</strong><br>\n10 (each) Single Arm DB Row<br>\n12 Banded Face Pulls<br>\n1min Long Lever Plank / RKC Plank</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HHGivxXIqEs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>5RFT: (Cap 15)</strong><br>\n10 Burpee Box Jumps 24/20\u2033<br>\n20 DB Snatchs 50/35#</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
