s<br>\nPlank</p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p>6RFR:</p>\n<p>45sec Wall Sit Hold (hips at parallel)</p>\n<p>-then going immediately in to:</p>\n<p>AMRAP 2<br>\n20 KB Swings (2/1.5pd)<br>\n30 Double Unders</p>\n<p>-then</p>\n<p>30sec Rest</p>\n<p>-Repeat 5 more times (6 total rounds)</p>\n<p><em>*IF you do NOT complete the 45 sec Wall Sit you can not collect reps during the AMRAP</em></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
