 lats, abdomen, and hips.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength:</h2>\n<p>EMOTM 10<br>\nOdd Minutes: 8 Strict Ring Dips<br>\nEven Minutes: 8 Strict Toes to Bar / Knees to Chest</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/I0mxljv5ozw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<h2>MetCon: (Cap 15)</h2>\n<p>Descending Ladder from 10 of:<br>\nBar Hop Burpees<br>\nPull-ups<br>\n10 OH Squats between each ROUND 45/35# (Scale to front squats)<br>\n<em>* workout starts w/ OHS</em></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
