quat</p>\n<h2>Strength: (20mins)</h2>\n<p><strong>Week 2: Front Squat \u2013 8RM</strong></p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201cHyuge\u201d</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1min ME Wall Balls 20/14#</strong></p>\n<p>\u2014go directly into</p>\n<p><strong>AMRAP 7</strong><br>\n20 Sit-ups<br>\n20 Alternating MB Slam 20/14#</p>\n<p>\u2014go directly into</p>\n<p><strong>1min ME Wall Balls</strong></p>\n<p><em>Score = total reps of everything</em></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
