develop any athlete\u2019s ability to generate power and drive force through the floor with the legs.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Strength: (20mins)</h2>\n<p><strong>Power Clean</strong><br>\nWeek 2: 3@50%, 3@60%, 3@70%, 3\u00d73@80% of (# from Week 1)</p>\n<h2>MetCon: (Cap 8)</h2>\n<p><strong>\u201cPants Suit\u201d</strong><br>\nSprint Chipper:<br>\n50 Alternating DB Snatch 50/35#<br>\n60 Step-ups 24/20\u2033<br>\n70 Du\u2019s</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
