retcontreras.com/the-rkc-plank/embed/#?secret=wtMzsmZ0Rf\" data-secret=\"wtMzsmZ0Rf\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" title=\"\u201cThe RKC Plank\u201d \u2014 Bret Contreras\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
