esn\u2019t start yet but today is a great time to practice the Power Clean before the series begins.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Skill:</h2>\n<p><strong>Clean and Jerk</strong></p>\n<h2>Strength:</h2>\n<p><strong>5\u00d73 Power Clean</strong><br>\n<em>*drop and reset, not touch and go</em></p>\n<h2>MetCon: AMRAP 15</h2>\n<p>5 Clean and Jerk 185/135#<br>\n10 Strict Pull-ups</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
