late Carry 45/35#<br>\n-then 3 rounds of<br>\n30 Stepback Lunges<br>\n30 DU\u2019s<br>\n-then<br>\n400m Plate Carry</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
