ict Pull-ups</p>\n<h2>MetCon:</h2>\n<p><strong>Double Death By:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EMOTM (+3) MB Cleans</strong><br>\n<em>* Once dead begin 2nd Death By on following minute</em></p>\n<p><strong>EMOTM (+1) Hand Release Push-up</strong><br>\n<em>* Once dead perform 30sec plank until class class is done</em></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!--article-content-wrap-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t   \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t</div>"}
